  "description": "Generation dashboard. Full §4.11 metric surface — header (TTFT/TPOT/throughput), overhead attribution (gateway vs worker), routing (direct-dispatch hits vs fallback by reason), admission (in-flight + KV reservation + rejected), grammar (compile latency + cache hit rate), failure modes (timeouts, cancellations, stale-attempt drops), saturation (per-worker flag), speculative decoding (acceptance rate when the speculative side-cell is active).",
