      "title": "TTFT p50 — gateway vs worker (ms)",
      "description": "Gap between the two lines is the NATS + queue overhead. Worker-side metric is observed inside the streaming adapter before any inter-process hop, so subtraction is honest given identical histogram buckets (TTFT_TPOT_BUCKETS).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ms"
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "max"
